        ================
        
        - Add support for Python3 (thanks @naxube)
        
        
        0.7 (2015-03-13)
        ================
        
        - Add Zetta and Yotta support (thanks @meteozond)
        - Fix bug with big values (fixes #8, thanks @meteozond)
        
        
